Enable Android Recovery Mode for uBoot
======================================

To enable recovery mode we need two things:

1) Flash boot.img and recovery.img instead of uImage + ramdisk.img

2) Support for booting from boot.img / recovery.img in the boot loader.

Point 1+2 will be taken care of by 0001-recovery-Enable-Android-recovery-mode.patch.

See http://wiki.stericsson.com/wiki/index.php/Android_Recovery_Mode for
more information about using Android Recovery Mode.
